iccdev provides CMake targets:

  find_package(RefIccMAX CONFIG REQUIRED)
  target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE RefIccMAX::IccProfLib2)

Optional feature targets are available when their features are installed:

  RefIccMAX::IccXML2
  RefIccMAX::IccJSON2

The vcpkg port builds static libraries only. Static-only installs also expose
explicit -static targets for installed libraries:

  RefIccMAX::IccProfLib2-static
  RefIccMAX::IccXML2-static
  RefIccMAX::IccJSON2-static
